usage:
    run it
    exposit: prints name and description
    elaborate: either here/from/to/creature/creatures
        - here: prints amount of creatures, and amounts of entries and exits
        - from: went from
        - to: go to
        - creature: info on specific creature (soon)
        - creatures: all creatures in area (soon)

